title: 3 Bedroom Home PLUS Office Ready for Rent
posting_body: ['VIRTUAL Tour available.', 'Located in sunny Oceanview, this charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath home, plus bonus office offers stylish modern interior design with lots of period charm.', 'Plenty of space and a flexible floor plan that lets you sleep and entertain on the top floor and work on the lower floor.', 'Easy access to highways 280 and 101.', 'Garage parking, laundry, storage, and large flat yard!', 'This house has it all and is available on August 15.', 'Tenants pay ALL UTILITIES, security deposit is $5000.', 'Top level:', '- Living room with original molding and decorative fireplace', '- Kitchen with 6 burner Thermador gas stove, stainless steel refrigerator, and new Kitchen Aid dishwasher, microwave, PLUS tons cabinet space!', '- Adjoining dining room overlooks the rear yard and has a large deck with a staircase leading down to the garden, an ideal spot for your morning cup of coffee!', '- 2 bedrooms, 1 facing the front of the house, the 2nd overlooking the yard.', '- Full bath with shower over tub and custom tile work', 'Lower level:', '- 3rd bedroom', '- Large office area (cannot be used as 4th bedroom)', '- Full-size washer and dryer', '- Tons of storage', '- Garage parking', '- Direct access to backyard', 'Other features:', '- Huge rear landscaped yard!', '- Hardwood floors', '- Decorative fireplace', '- Double-paned windows in the front', '- New Furnace', '- Electrical outlets with built-in USB-ports', '- LED lighting throughout']
